{"tid":1142853,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"柒頭網民鬧《東張西望》趕走大陸人好多事 黃愷怡BB好慘慘豬","createTime":"2019-05-07T10:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T09:59:43.000Z","uid":57898,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f8834264b26939ccd8f8dbff9b236d97f6b4a615","tid":1142853,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:56:23.000Z","msg":"適逢一連4日「五一黃金周」高峰期間，大批大陸遊客自由行竟然不去尖沙咀、旺角逛街，反而湧去「打卡勝地」老牌屋邨彩虹邨、香港中文大學影相。惟人實在太多，中港矛盾愈來愈深，不僅居民打不到波，未能正常使用屋邨設施，聲浪之大也明顯影響學生溫書，嚴重滋擾港人日常生活。商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華在商台節目上表示，所有城市歡迎遊客，雖然明知會無可避免影響港人生活，但這是全球現象，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">他希望港人應以同理心面對</span>，有關單位幫助管理人數等，就可以解決問題：「用同理心相信唔係唔可以不能解決。」，惹起更多港人不滿。於是《東張西望》再出動，派出攝製隊及女主持黃愷怡直擊大陸遊客讓屋邨、大學淪陷真相，期間女主持看不過眼開口窒到其中一個青年無聲出，被網民大讚智慧與美貌並重。<br />\n<br />\n大陸人入侵大學屋邨 打卡呃like文化滋擾港人 <br />\n<br />\n近年大陸遊客來港已經逐漸改變旅遊模式，以前愛拖行李箱到金鋪、藥房爆買，如今轉攻進行深度遊覽，尋找本地特別地方打卡，再將大作放在社交平台小紅書呃like，教國內同胞如何攻略各大秘景。隨着網上資訊流通，不少人會於旅遊前搜尋香港資訊，所以五彩繽粉的彩虹邨成為最新熱門打卡聖地。結果每逢假期，就有大批大陸遊客佔領彩虹邨，去到黃金周仲誇張，對正經過大翻新樓宇的公共空間一度湧入了近400名遊客，當中以大陸遊客為多數，部分人甚至拖著行李箱，四處擺pose影相。他們阻礙居民打波不特止，還阻塞出入口，令居民未能正常出入；亦有屋邨「冬菇亭」及街市淪為大陸團團餐地點及景點，人頭湧湧，搞到公廁不時排長龍，居民投訴環境衞生欠佳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FRykyTb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFRykyTb.png&h=85b4314c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，不少中文大學大陸來港學生以分享留學體驗為賣點，做兼職導遊無牌帶團，每名遊客收費由200多港元至1200多港元不等，每小時賺近1000元，非常受大陸遊客歡迎，所以中文大學都相告淪陷，連新亞書院的天人合一亭也成為最新打卡熱點。可是大陸遊客入侵校園問題多多，先是迫爆校巴、佔用學生飯堂等設施，旅行團又製造嘈雜噪音，嚴重滋擾正準備考試的學生，連住在宿舍的學生作息亦受到騷擾。中文大學學生會會長蘇浚鋒表示，校方曾規管旅遊巴入校園的數量，但在黃金周到訪的多為個人遊大陸遊客，制止不了，故曾收到同學投訴指校巴及餐廳被旅客佔用：「依家正值考試時間，合一亭附近宿舍會有遊客喧嘩戲水。」《東張西望》今次由黃愷怡出擊，實地觀察情況。黃愷怡一到埗就見到天一合一亭旁邊已經排滿遊客，跟學生人數差不多，有些是大陸中小學生大約20、30人，大媽就10多人一團，他們都在大學玩到忘了形。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7dc12MA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7dc12MA.png&h=38b6bc78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女主持睇唔過眼用一招反擊<br />\n<br />\n上次有阮嘉敏在屯門公園塞到大陸中佬、大媽無聲出，今次女主持換了黃愷怡........<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/106aV67.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F106aV67.png&h=15e43b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本身呢篇野睇到火滾<br />\n點撚知有條柒頭為大陸人幫口 話《東張西望》<br />\n點都要幫佢出下名<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cBiky3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cBiky3.png&h=c529347c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6955598df9b4c8e3700e8be778128b3d89bebca7","tid":1142853,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:56:51.000Z","msg":"來源：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2344981/ref?=fb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2344981%2Fref%3F%3Dfb&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=d89bbdb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2344981/ref?=fb</a>"},{"pid":"e5bd85f0816ab851c660f27e9e4af80bedeb80aa","tid":1142853,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:57:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"968ea96cdaffa949f590637986aaecf0273def9d","tid":1142853,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:58:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"527a70d2bd6c588de93054abe21d15bf0f6f447a","tid":1142853,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:59:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9fc281c83246c116db60ccbe0372083bca861d53","tid":1142853,"uid":57898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:00:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c7d2fe8a497cf2a111e62073b1ca85fa6053e884","tid":1142853,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"de586b08e2fc8fe8c6e1232af2c37450d71dccfb","tid":1142853,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:01:13.000Z","msg":"要求帶團到半山深水灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f03a0f3d42dc662311c069e453a3d9833a47e4e","tid":1142853,"uid":113373,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:03:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n星期六 早上9點 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"99e566e8ba0efb0b5f9368fad2217c4e22c897ab","tid":1142853,"uid":154907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"Inspiration <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2c66355d29ce27b292799278ef4818d33e3c8d","tid":1142853,"uid":90735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:07:51.000Z","msg":"去習總香港物業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83c607f9cc89080fb0740d167243641d37e04ef","tid":1142853,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc440a2c151500201d164d58066637b2864bcff1","tid":1142853,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:26:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ab7263865ab1dd1c3eb904a20b4ae71d1c396228","tid":1142853,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"Jasmin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bf773a896806cd88df4e686b3e27a1a339746b","tid":1142853,"uid":57898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab7263865ab1dd1c3eb904a20b4ae71d1c396228","tid":1142853,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"Jasmin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"好靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6cd41e827fdac184a5fa87221cf04eb6cc84266","tid":1142853,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:10:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ac634cfa9a0fe37f7820737edb03ceed67cee1ac","tid":1142853,"uid":36722,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f7560c523b755e6e2af234cd3d86a436e07ee7","tid":1142853,"uid":57898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ac634cfa9a0fe37f7820737edb03ceed67cee1ac","tid":1142853,"uid":36722,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:23:20.000Z","msg":"你咁鬧都冇用 你睇下網民 依然係唔撚信 你不如係佢下面留言仲好la"},{"pid":"1dfe5bb3c87daaa5b88c9c2608fd2a7f12dd1d7c","tid":1142853,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:31:56.000Z","msg":"搵手足起下呢位網民底 唔使多 知佢住邊度夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再利用網絡力量推介鄰國文青去嗰度打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73b7330a246a9be4d70e7ccfb97417545d6416c","tid":1142853,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:59:43.000Z","msg":"呢隻黃海馬係矜貴得起嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}